    "Step 2 A fuzzy comparison matrix 24 can be made by converting pairwise comparisons into crisp values.",
    "Equation (3) can be used to generate a normalized fuzzy matrix.",
    "Step 3 The proposed model presents a new method of utilizing the Hybrid Pythagorean fuzzy AHP methodology to generate a weighted priority matrix.",
